description:
#yogamusic #meditate #meditionmusic #emotionalpiano

„Daydream“ is a very calm and emotional Piano Solo composition in New Age / Neoclassical Genre. 
The Sound reminds to Music from Nils Frahm or Ludovico Einaudi.
